{"tid":1743041,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"全民捐血日","createTime":"2019-11-21T04:46:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T07:47:36.000Z","uid":269159,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2bf34495104e1540b2931066ca096a6a2b76e002","tid":1743041,"uid":269159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:46:44.000Z","msg":"為咗展現高質民意反極權，而遊行/集會/以武制暴 只係展現民意其中抗爭方式<br />\n<br />\n有人話抗爭要融入生活，呢類運動正好食正個理念<br />\n<br />\n與其我地有咁多人 不如一齊做善事 比全世界人知道 「我們不是暴徒，而係充滿愛心，愛香港既香港人」<br />\n因此我有一個建議：<br />\n<br />\n一齊去做有意義 亦對社會有實質貢獻工作<br />\n例如 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全民捐血</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前成日聽到血庫唔夠血 要 呼籲捐血<br />\n不如就一齊去啦，因為多區都有捐血站，個行為等於開花，不過係善事開花，相信能夠<br />\n正面地展現抗爭可愛一面<br />\n<br />\n一日捐唔晒 就下星期再捐，捐到血庫爆為止！<br />\n<br />\n唯一係安全考慮，因為要登記ID先可以捐血，所以全日係以和理非姿態進行，以免比狗咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果覺得可以請幫推同埋研究文宣同set日程，sorry因為我唔識搞文宣呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n參考各區捐血站<br />\n<a href=\"https://www5.ha.org.hk/rcbts/hkarticle.asp?bid=85&amp;MenuID=5#.Xc9TfyV-WaM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww5.ha.org.hk%2Frcbts%2Fhkarticle.asp%3Fbid%3D85%26MenuID%3D5%23.Xc9TfyV-WaM&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameMsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=9552d16d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www5.ha.org.hk/rcbts/hkarticle.asp?bid=85&amp;MenuID=5#.Xc9TfyV-WaM</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mOGe4K5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmOGe4K5.jpg&h=61ee89b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n搞個暗黑全民日笑下：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />全民捐精日<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"807a0979e27088676c139f4c4d934fc645496c2b","tid":1743041,"uid":229289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:47:21.000Z","msg":"好多二噁英 血庫收唔收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2466296bb5f14629fb75a45be8b00eeefd4702e4","tid":1743041,"uid":338636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:49:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>一齊入嚟睇致勝關鍵！！！！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n[拒絕分化！]古人一早教我地點贏<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1739422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1739422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n[正能量撚]出去之前，希望你可以睇下呢個po<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1734559\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1734559</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>全個連登都係負能量，我要你地有正能量啊</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"f8c40930ec10a3c0fd203c7c8a6d78ab615f5f4f","tid":1743041,"uid":269159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:47:26.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"1b169314c5ab6078e7c9deb12b1322688fd983ce","tid":1743041,"uid":269159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:47:36.000Z","msg":"自推"}]}